    dc:description "FIGURE 107. Chaetocnema pusaensis. A Female habitus. B Head, frontal view. C Pronotum and peri-scutellar area. D Aedeagus of Paralectotype, ventral view. E Aedeagus of Paralectotype, lateral view. F Apex of aedeagus, ventral view (Paralectotype). G Vaginal palpi. H Spermatheca. I Tignum. J Pygidium (tergite 7) of female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3543274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

